---
description: Grabby architecture and coding rules
globs:
  - "apps/**/*.ts"
  - "packages/**/*.ts"
alwaysApply: true
---

- TypeScript strict mode is required.
- Avoid `any` unless explicitly justified.
- Keep extraction business logic inside `packages/core`.
- `apps/api` only orchestrates rendering and response handling.
- `apps/web` remains static-first and accessible.
- Use kebab-case for files and folders.
